/* fonts */
export const FontFamily = {
  basicRegular: "Basic_regular",
  titleH416: "Inria Sans_bold",
  bodySmall13: "Inria Sans_regular",
  text: "Rubik_regular",
  title: "Rubik_medium",
  hindSiliguriRegular: "Hind Siliguri_regular",
  hindSiliguriSemibold: "Hind Siliguri_semibold",
  mulishBold: "Mulish_bold",
  poppinsBold: "Poppins_bold",
};
/* font sizes */
export const FontSize = {
  size_base: 16,
  title_size: 18,
  bodySmall13_size: 12,
  titleH416_size: 14,
  bodyMedium15_size: 15,
  size_smi: 13,
  titleH320_size: 20,
  size_7xl: 26,
  size_9xl: 28,
  size_5xl: 24,
  size_3xs: 10,
  size_4xl: 23,
};
/* Colors */
export const Color = {
  whitesmoke_100: "#f8f8f8",
  whitesmoke_200: "#f7f7f7",
  gray6: "#f2f2f2",
  green: "#009f0b",
  black: "#000",
  textLight: "#fff",
  card: "#fcfffe",
  gray_100: "#807a7a",
  gray_200: "#242424",
  gray_300: "#222",
  textDark: "#1c162e",
  gray_400: "#191919",
  colorTypographyTitle: "#120d26",
  gray_500: "#060518",
  gray_600: "rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7)",
  gray_700: "rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1)",
  textGrey: "#c6c4ca",
  secondaryRed: "#ff3a79",
  crimson_100: "#ff0a38",
  pink: "#ff678b",
  colorTypographyParagraph: "#3c3e56",
  dimgray: "#706d6d",
  gainsboro_100: "#e0e0e0",
  gainsboro_200: "#d8d8d8",
  slategray_100: "#747688",
  indianred: "#eb5757",
};
/* Paddings */
export const Padding = {
  p_xs: 12,
  p_sm: 14,
  p_3xl: 22,
  p_base: 16,
  p_5xs: 8,
  p_121xl_7: 141,
};
/* border radiuses */
export const Border = {
  br_31xl: 50,
  br_xs: 12,
  br_37xl: 56,
  br_base: 16,
  br_3xs: 10,
  br_5xs: 8,
  br_sm: 14,
  br_19xl: 38,
  br_11xs_3: 1,
  br_10xs_7: 3,
  br_7xs: 6,
  br_12xs: 1,
  br_11xs_5: 2,
  br_12xs_4: 0,
  br_xl: 20,
  br_9xl: 28,
};
